sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.flight_number, '"'||v0.airline_code||'"',
 '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', v0.departure_time, '"'||v0.flight_id||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = 'AA') 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'CHICAGO'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'PHILADELPHIA'))) AND (v0.departure_time =  1800))));
